  "description": "<h3>💰 <strong>Salary & Benefits</strong></h3><p>⭐ <strong>Salary: $2,280 – $2,450 (excluding ot)</strong><br />⭐ <strong>Yearly Increment </strong><br />⭐ <strong>Incentive Bonuses (KPI + OT)</strong><br />⭐ <strong>AWS + Variable Bonus (1–2 months)</strong><br />⭐ <strong>Medical Claims Provided</strong><br />✅<em><strong> </strong></em><strong>Stable permanent role </strong><br /></p><p><strong>--------------------------------------------------</strong></p><h3>⏰ <strong>Working Hours (Only 15 days/month!)</strong></h3><p>🔄 <strong>4-3-3-4 Shift Cycle</strong><br />🌙 <strong>12-hour Day /Night Shift (7am–7pm / 7pm–7am)</strong><br />🚍 <strong>Direct Bus Access From:</strong><br />Tampines / Punggol / Sengkang / Hougang / Pasir Ris</p><h3>🔧 Job Scope:</h3><ul><li>Product <strong>assembly & basic quality checks</strong></li><li><strong>Picking & packing</strong> finished goods</li><li><strong>Loading & unloading</strong> tasks</li><li>Able to handle heavy lifting</li></ul><h3>--------------------------------------</h3><h3>📌 Requirements:</h3><ul><li>Singaporeans ONLY</li><li><strong>No Experience Required! </strong></li><li>Full Training Provided</li></ul><p>------------------------------</p><p><strong>Whatsapp 8500 3939 Janice</strong></p><p>-------</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Chin Jia Hui, Janice<br />EA Personnel No: R22107485<br />EA License No: 15C7752</p>",
